I can’t believe it’s been almost a year since I made my move to Goa 🌴
This move honestly really made me discover so many things about myself. Just sharing a few gigs where I got to perform with some wonderful artists at amazing venues ❤️

Got a chance to perform with a live band @tingishika @kavin_music at one of my fav venues @hideaway.goa , with UK based Ghanaian rapper  @bryte_music @achhra.in at @elephantandco_india , with @generalzooz for @skankit.in.. big up @sanyas_i , workshops @goasunsplash and #tvsmotosoul @tvsracing_official , and with my fam and crew @iriedancecrew with the baddest @djchiquidubs from Panama and our very own @sukanya.music at @goasunsplash 😍❤️

On to the next chapter but I’ll be back soon 🌴
